WEBVTT

00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:40.580
=Reincarnated Love=

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:43.700
=Episode 16=

00:00:45.150 --> 00:00:45.990
Huaijin,

00:00:46.080 --> 00:00:46.920
let Ruoli go.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:48.390
We can talk at home.

00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:54.640
Yuan, don't worry.

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:55.750
I won't hurt you.

00:00:56.110 --> 00:00:57.670
Lu Huaijin, stop this madness.

00:00:58.240 --> 00:00:59.080
Yuan,

00:00:59.560 --> 00:01:00.400
I don't care.

00:01:00.750 --> 00:01:01.640
Today,

00:01:01.960 --> 00:01:03.240
I'll make sure he dies here.

00:01:03.310 --> 00:01:04.160
You...

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:05.120
Huaijin,

00:01:05.680 --> 00:01:06.530
don't harm her.

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:07.380
Silence!

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:10.040
There's no turning back now.

00:01:10.480 --> 00:01:11.510
Surrender.

00:01:11.510 --> 00:01:12.360
Shut up!

00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:13.240
Huo Linchuan!

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:15.040
Do you know how much I despise you?

00:01:16.230 --> 00:01:17.680
Why must you treat me this way?

00:01:18.790 --> 00:01:19.870
Yanzhi,

00:01:20.070 --> 00:01:21.400
my dearest brother.

00:01:23.070 --> 00:01:24.480
Seeing you like this

00:01:25.040 --> 00:01:26.120
truly brings me joy.

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:28.640
When did you become like this?

00:01:29.280 --> 00:01:30.400
All our lives,

00:01:30.400 --> 00:01:31.560
Father only ever saw you.

00:01:31.790 --> 00:01:33.470
All the family property
was meant for you.

00:01:34.120 --> 00:01:34.960
And now,

00:01:35.790 --> 00:01:37.280
even the heart of the girl I love

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:38.480
leans toward you as well.

00:01:38.680 --> 00:01:39.560
Why is that?

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:41.950
How am I lesser than you?

00:01:42.840 --> 00:01:44.870
Be it cunning or talent,

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:47.680
I am the one who deserves it all.

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:50.400
If you want power

00:01:50.560 --> 00:01:51.400
or influence,

00:01:51.710 --> 00:01:52.870
I can share it with you.

00:01:53.280 --> 00:01:54.400
All of this can be discussed.

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:55.660
Put down the knife first.

00:01:56.430 --> 00:01:57.270
Share?

00:01:58.680 --> 00:01:59.920
Is that charity, then?

00:02:00.760 --> 00:02:02.040
I want everything.

00:02:02.350 --> 00:02:03.310
I want everyone

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:05.350
to bow at my feet,

00:02:06.010 --> 00:02:06.870
especially you,

00:02:06.870 --> 00:02:07.710
Huo Linchuan.

00:02:08.050 --> 00:02:08.960
Lu Huaijin,

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:10.280
you've lost your mind.

00:02:12.630 --> 00:02:13.910
I've lost my mind?

00:02:14.630 --> 00:02:15.680
Is that how you see me?

00:02:17.870 --> 00:02:18.960
Huo Linchuan,

00:02:19.470 --> 00:02:22.080
you and your righteous father

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:23.030
are both so false.

00:02:23.030 --> 00:02:24.190
It makes me sick.

00:02:24.840 --> 00:02:26.430
Since you first joined my family,

00:02:26.960 --> 00:02:28.840
my father treated you as his own.

00:02:29.470 --> 00:02:30.360
When did he ever

00:02:31.400 --> 00:02:33.240
treat you unfairly?

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:34.750
Huo Wenyuan

00:02:35.560 --> 00:02:36.800
is nothing but a hypocrite.

00:02:38.080 --> 00:02:40.080
He pretends to be honorable,

00:02:40.430 --> 00:02:42.190
but he actually deceived my mother.

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:44.960
My mother was so devoted to him.

00:02:45.190 --> 00:02:46.523
Even as she drew her last breath,

00:02:47.560 --> 00:02:49.150
she was still calling his name.

00:02:57.740 --> 00:03:00.940
(Huo)

00:03:16.190 --> 00:03:18.310
Mother, are you all right?

00:03:18.680 --> 00:03:20.520
Mother, are you okay?

00:03:21.360 --> 00:03:22.200
Mother.

00:03:23.560 --> 00:03:24.750
Yunzhou,

00:03:24.750 --> 00:03:26.870
take this identity token.

00:03:27.400 --> 00:03:29.470
(Huo)
Go see Duke Huo.

00:03:29.750 --> 00:03:32.150
He will know who you are.

00:03:34.030 --> 00:03:35.030
Go.

00:03:38.240 --> 00:03:39.150
Mother.

00:03:39.710 --> 00:03:40.550
Mother.

00:03:42.120 --> 00:03:42.960
Mother...

00:03:42.960 --> 00:03:45.820
(Huo Mansion)

00:03:47.560 --> 00:03:48.870
You little beggar.

00:03:49.080 --> 00:03:51.030
How dare you try to cling to the Duke?

00:03:51.280 --> 00:03:53.430
You even claim to be his son?

00:03:54.480 --> 00:03:55.390
You brat.

00:03:55.430 --> 00:03:56.280
Get out of here.

00:04:16.580 --> 00:04:19.100
(Huo)

00:04:22.070 --> 00:04:22.910
Come here.

00:04:30.750 --> 00:04:31.630
As for you,

00:04:32.430 --> 00:04:33.680
you are his legitimate heir,

00:04:33.830 --> 00:04:36.070
born to the esteemed lady
of noble birth.

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:39.160
You had everything I longed for
when you were born.

00:04:39.160 --> 00:04:41.160
Why is that?

00:04:43.430 --> 00:04:45.240
Whose child is this? So adorable.

00:04:45.620 --> 00:04:47.030
I miss you so much.

00:04:50.870 --> 00:04:51.950
Well done.

00:04:52.310 --> 00:04:53.600
Up you go!

00:04:53.720 --> 00:04:54.560
Higher!

00:04:55.720 --> 00:04:56.560
Even higher!

00:04:57.310 --> 00:04:58.190
Straighten your back.

00:04:58.190 --> 00:04:59.270
Hold your head high.

00:04:59.600 --> 00:05:00.870
The mighty tiger.

00:05:03.190 --> 00:05:04.750
Up you go!

00:05:05.270 --> 00:05:06.160
Straighten your back.

00:05:10.070 --> 00:05:13.360
What I can no longer bear is

00:05:13.630 --> 00:05:16.360
Ruoli becoming your bride.

00:05:16.630 --> 00:05:18.750
I saw you two being all lovey-dovey.

00:05:18.870 --> 00:05:20.040
I saw her shed tears for you

00:05:20.040 --> 00:05:21.040
and worry for your sake.

00:05:21.480 --> 00:05:24.630
Who should I seek to settle this hatred?

00:05:25.600 --> 00:05:26.560
Therefore,

00:05:28.190 --> 00:05:30.240
you framed my father for treason,

00:05:30.750 --> 00:05:32.830
ordered Jiang Huaikang
to kill Ruoli's father,

00:05:34.040 --> 00:05:36.040
and repeatedly put me
in deadly situations.

00:05:36.870 --> 00:05:38.630
Was it all for this imagined hatred?

00:05:38.630 --> 00:05:39.630
I don't care!

00:05:41.160 --> 00:05:42.870
Seeing you struggling

00:05:43.430 --> 00:05:45.040
and losing the one you love

00:05:45.480 --> 00:05:47.040
is my greatest satisfaction.

00:05:52.950 --> 00:05:54.360
Losing the one I love?

00:05:55.480 --> 00:05:56.600
Have you forgotten?

00:05:57.680 --> 00:05:58.950
As I told you before,

00:05:59.870 --> 00:06:02.060
Jiang Ruoli is just a pawn to me.

00:06:03.070 --> 00:06:05.750
I used her to make you show
your true colors

00:06:06.950 --> 00:06:08.480
and tell the truth.

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:12.480
Now that she's served her purpose,

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:15.750
does the player really care

00:06:16.480 --> 00:06:18.920
about a pawn?

00:06:21.630 --> 00:06:22.870
What do you mean?

00:06:23.750 --> 00:06:24.950
Drop the act.

00:06:25.390 --> 00:06:26.630
Come at me if you dare.

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:29.630
Do you really think
I'd hesitate to kill her?

00:06:30.040 --> 00:06:30.950
Go ahead.

00:06:35.750 --> 00:06:37.430
Come closer!

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:39.240
Alright.

00:06:46.870 --> 00:06:47.870
If you won't act,

00:06:48.830 --> 00:06:49.670
I will.

00:06:51.750 --> 00:06:52.590
Dear,

00:06:53.950 --> 00:06:55.170
I'm sorry you've had to suffer.

00:06:55.310 --> 00:06:56.480
Huo Linchuan, you...

00:06:56.920 --> 00:06:58.000
Come here!

00:07:10.610 --> 00:07:11.460
Are you alright?

00:07:11.510 --> 00:07:12.350
I'm fine.

00:07:12.480 --> 00:07:13.430
What I just said...

00:07:13.430 --> 00:07:15.240
I know; it was part of the plan.

00:07:19.800 --> 00:07:22.800
Watching this truly unsettles me.

00:07:26.870 --> 00:07:28.630
Since I can't have her,

00:07:28.950 --> 00:07:30.510
neither can you.

00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:32.000
Watch out!

00:07:44.800 --> 00:07:45.640
Yanzhi!

00:07:46.750 --> 00:07:47.590
Yanzhi...

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:51.760
Yanzhi...

00:07:55.270 --> 00:07:56.120
Yanzhi...

00:07:56.870 --> 00:07:57.870
Don't frighten me.

00:08:01.070 --> 00:08:01.910
Ruoli...

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:03.870
I once promised

00:08:05.270 --> 00:08:07.070
to keep you safe for a lifetime.

00:08:16.070 --> 00:08:17.560
Yanzhi...

00:08:18.040 --> 00:08:19.480
you'll be alright.

00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:20.960
Yanzhi!

00:08:21.600 --> 00:08:22.440
Yanzhi...

00:08:23.430 --> 00:08:24.270
Yanzhi...

00:08:27.160 --> 00:08:28.680
♪The dream shattered♪

00:08:29.040 --> 00:08:30.720
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:32.360
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:08:32.440 --> 00:08:33.670
It's all my fault.

00:08:35.120 --> 00:08:36.360
It's all my fault.

00:08:38.150 --> 00:08:39.240
Yanzhi.

00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:41.240
Yanzhi.

00:08:42.840 --> 00:08:45.680
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:08:46.910 --> 00:08:48.240
Yanzhi...

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:51.510
Yanzhi...

00:08:51.680 --> 00:08:53.200
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:08:53.600 --> 00:08:57.160
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:08:57.910 --> 00:08:59.150
It's all my fault.

00:08:59.840 --> 00:09:03.560
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:09:04.790 --> 00:09:06.360
It's all my fault.

00:09:06.870 --> 00:09:08.390
I swear here and now:

00:09:08.970 --> 00:09:10.080
For all the remaining years,

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:12.440
I'll do everything to keep you safe

00:09:13.360 --> 00:09:14.360
and never abandon you.

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:18.120
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:09:18.280 --> 00:09:19.680
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:09:19.680 --> 00:09:22.800
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:09:22.880 --> 00:09:24.320
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:09:25.440 --> 00:09:26.750
Yanzhi.

00:09:28.920 --> 00:09:30.930
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:09:30.960 --> 00:09:32.160
Yanzhi...

00:09:32.170 --> 00:09:34.840
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:09:35.160 --> 00:09:39.560
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:09:39.800 --> 00:09:42.720
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:09:42.840 --> 00:09:47.280
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:09:47.480 --> 00:09:53.200
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:10:14.410 --> 00:10:15.930
♪The dream shattered♪

00:10:16.290 --> 00:10:17.970
♪Like illusion, yet true♪

00:10:17.970 --> 00:10:19.610
♪Like a restless soul♪

00:10:20.490 --> 00:10:22.050
♪How vague♪

00:10:22.450 --> 00:10:23.970
♪Rain and blood, drifting wild♪

00:10:23.970 --> 00:10:26.210
♪A blade of frost in dreams♪

00:10:27.010 --> 00:10:29.610
♪Love and hate entwined♪

00:10:30.090 --> 00:10:32.930
♪Rise and fall, yet never fade♪

00:10:33.570 --> 00:10:38.330
♪How can I turn the tides
of this fleeting life♪

00:10:38.930 --> 00:10:40.450
♪When fate falls apart♪

00:10:40.850 --> 00:10:44.410
♪Memories return,
carving tears upon my face♪

00:10:45.130 --> 00:10:46.690
♪Yet I can't hold on♪

00:10:47.090 --> 00:10:50.810
♪Only warmth remains
where longing once burned♪

00:10:51.530 --> 00:10:54.370
♪Life after life♪

00:10:54.850 --> 00:10:57.530
♪Fated to meet, but never meant to be♪

00:10:58.170 --> 00:11:02.250
♪Still, I refuse to bow or yield♪

00:11:02.330 --> 00:11:05.370
♪In this life, love becomes my blade♪

00:11:05.530 --> 00:11:06.930
♪To break free from reincarnation♪

00:11:06.930 --> 00:11:10.050
♪All past affairs tangled with regret♪

00:11:10.130 --> 00:11:11.570
♪Now shatter apart♪

00:11:11.690 --> 00:11:15.450
♪By fate and karmic ties confined♪

00:11:16.170 --> 00:11:18.970
♪Is this fate or calamity♪

00:11:19.250 --> 00:11:22.090
♪Is it life, death, or parting pain♪

00:11:22.410 --> 00:11:26.810
♪I ask only for a moment of peace,
as devout as my heart♪

00:11:27.050 --> 00:11:29.970
♪In the next life, grant me one kiss♪

00:11:30.090 --> 00:11:34.530
♪To kiss the snow upon the brows,
and the depths of your gaze♪

00:11:34.730 --> 00:11:40.450
♪For once we kissed,
destiny bound us to never part♪

00:11:40.890 --> 00:11:43.610
♪This fleeting life feels but a dream♪

00:11:43.850 --> 00:11:46.570
♪Sober or indulge♪

00:11:47.010 --> 00:11:53.010
♪I only wish to be with you,
with all my heart♪